ModelResponse(parts=[TextPart(content='{\n  "sparql_query": "PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>\\nPREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>\\nPREFIX s223: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>\\nPREFIX ex: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223/data/lbnl-example-2#>\\n\\nSELECT DISTINCT ?zone ?zoneLabel ?property ?propertyLabel WHERE {\\n  # Zone instances\\n  ?zone a s223:Zone .\\n\\n  # Directly associated property (if any)\\n  OPTIONAL { ?zone s223:hasProperty ?property . }\\n\\n  # Indirect association via a RoomDomainSpace (or any DomainSpace that is a RoomDomainSpace)\\n  OPTIONAL {\\n    ?zone s223:hasDomainSpace ?ds .\\n    ?ds a ex:RoomDomainSpace .\\n    ?ds s223:hasProperty ?property .\\n  }\\n\\n  # Keep only zones that have at least one property via either path\\n  FILTER(BOUND(?property))\\n\\n  OPTIONAL { ?zone rdfs:label ?zoneLabel . }\\n  OPTIONAL { ?property rdfs:label ?propertyLabel . }\\n}\\nORDER BY ?zone\\nLIMIT 200"\n}', part_kind='text')], model_name='hosted_vllm/hosted_vllm/gpt-oss-120b', timestamp=datetime.datetime(2026, 1, 22, 7, 42, 34, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), kind='response')

PREFIX brick: <https://brickschema.org/schema/Brick/>
PREFIX s223: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>

SELECT ?property ?alcEndpoint ?mpcDb
WHERE {
  # Find zones
  ?zone a s223:Zone .
  # Properties associated with the zone
  ?zone s223:hasProperty ?property .
  # Consider observable/actuatable quantifiable properties
  ?property a ?propClass .
  FILTER(?propClass IN (s223:QuantifiableObservableProperty, s223:QuantifiableActuatableProperty))
  
  # Filter non‑editable properties (writable missing or false)
  OPTIONAL { ?property brick:writable ?writable . }
  FILTER( !BOUND(?writable) || ?writable = "False"^^xsd:string )
  
  # Retrieve ALC endpoint and MPC DB name if present
  OPTIONAL { ?property brick:endpoint ?alcEndpoint . }
  OPTIONAL { ?property brick:mpc_db_name ?mpcDb . }
}
LIMIT 100

ModelResponse(parts=[TextPart(content='{\n  "sparql_query": "PREFIX brick: <https://brickschema.org/schema/Brick/>\\nPREFIX r223: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>\\nPREFIX ex: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223/data/lbnl-example-2#>\\nPREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>\\n\\nSELECT DISTINCT ?rtu ?property ?endpoint ?mpcDbName WHERE {\\n  # Identify each RTU air‑handling unit (UFT in the LBNL example)\\n  ?rtu a ex:UFT .\\n  \\n  # Get the properties attached to the RTU (any property class)\\n  ?rtu r223:hasProperty ?property .\\n  \\n  # Each property can have an external reference describing where its data lives\\n  ?property brick:externalReference ?extRef .\\n  \\n  # We only want the *non‑writable* external references\\n  ?extRef brick:writable \\"False\\"^^xsd:string .\\n  \\n  # Retrieve the ALC endpoint (SOAP API) and the MPC database name, when present\\n  OPTIONAL { ?extRef brick:endpoint ?endpoint . }\\n  OPTIONAL { ?extRef brick:mpc_db_name ?mpcDbName . }\\n  \\n  # Keep only those refs that actually provide an endpoint and an MPC name\\n  FILTER (bound(?endpoint) && bound(?mpcDbName))\\n}\\nORDER BY ?rtu ?property"\n}', part_kind='text')], model_name='hosted_vllm/hosted_vllm/gpt-oss-120b', timestamp=datetime.datetime(2026, 1, 22, 7, 52, 9, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), kind='response')

generated_sparql:
PREFIX s223: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>
PREFIX brick: <https://brickschema.org/schema/Brick/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?rtu ?property ?endpoint ?mpcDb
WHERE {
  # RTU air handling units
  ?rtu a s223:AirHandlingUnit .

  # Their properties (observable or actuatable)
  ?rtu s223:hasProperty ?property .

  # External reference for the property
  ?property s223:hasExternalReference ?extRef .

  # Endpoint URLs and MPC DB names
  OPTIONAL { ?extRef brick:endpoint ?endpoint . }
  OPTIONAL { ?extRef brick:mpc_db_name ?mpcDb . }

  # Determine if the external reference is writable (default to false if not present)
  OPTIONAL { ?extRef brick:writable ?writable . }
  FILTER (BOUND(?endpoint) && ( !BOUND(?writable) || ?writable = false ))
}
ORDER BY ?rtu ?property

ModelResponse(parts=[TextPart(content='{\n  "sparql_query": "PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>\\nPREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>\\nPREFIX brick: <https://brickschema.org/schema/Brick/>\\nPREFIX std223: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>\\n\\nSELECT ?propertyLabel ?endpointURI\\nWHERE {\\n  # Find RTU units (identified by a label containing \\"RTU\\")\\n  ?rtu rdfs:label ?rtuLabel .\\n  FILTER regex(?rtuLabel, \\"RTU\\", \\"i\\") .\\n\\n  # RTU has properties (observable or actuatable)\\n  ?rtu std223:hasProperty ?prop .\\n\\n  # Each property may expose an API endpoint\\n  ?prop brick:endpoint ?endpointURI .\\n\\n  # Determine if the endpoint is writable; if the triple is missing or false, treat as read‑only\\n  OPTIONAL { ?endpointURI brick:writable ?writable . }\\n  FILTER ( !bound(?writable) || ?writable = false )\\n\\n  # Get a friendly label for the property (if any)\\n  OPTIONAL { ?prop rdfs:label ?propertyLabel . }\\n  BIND ( COALESCE(?propertyLabel, STRAFTER(STR(?prop), \\"#\\")) AS ?propertyLabel )\\n}\\nORDER BY ?propertyLabel\\nLIMIT 100"\n}', part_kind='text')], model_name='hosted_vllm/hosted_vllm/gpt-oss-120b', timestamp=datetime.datetime(2026, 1, 22, 7, 52, 38, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), kind='response')

ground_truth_sparql:
PREFIX ref: <https://brickschema.org/schema/Brick/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX s223: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>
SELECT DISTINCT ?target ?prop ?label ?qty ?ref ?alc_endpoint ?mpc_endpoint where {
?target a s223:WatertoWaterHeatPump .
?target s223:contains ?prop .
?prop rdfs:label ?label .
?prop s223:observes ?qty .
?qty s223:hasExternalReference ?ref .
?ref ref:endpoint ?alc_endpoint .
?ref ref:mpc_db_name ?mpc_endpoint .
?ref ref:writable "False" .
}

PREFIX s223: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>
PREFIX brick: <https://brickschema.org/schema/Brick/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>

SELECT ?heatPump ?heatPumpLabel ?property ?propertyLabel ?ref ?endpoint
WHERE {
  # Instances of Water‑to‑Water Heat Pump
  ?heatPump a s223:WatertoWaterHeatPump .
  OPTIONAL { ?heatPump rdfs:label ?heatPumpLabel . }

  # Observable quantifiable properties of the heat pump
  ?heatPump s223:hasProperty ?property .
  ?property a s223:QuantifiableObservableProperty .
  OPTIONAL { ?property rdfs:label ?propertyLabel . }

  # Keep only non‑writable properties (either missing writable flag or explicitly false)
  OPTIONAL { ?property brick:writable ?writable . }
  FILTER ( !bound(?writable) || ?writable = false )

  # Property must reference an external endpoint
  ?property brick:source ?ref .
  ?ref brick:endpoint ?endpoint .
}
LIMIT 100

ground_truth_sparql:
PREFIX ref: <https://brickschema.org/schema/Brick/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX s223: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>
SELECT DISTINCT ?target ?prop ?label ?qty ?ref ?alc_endpoint ?mpc_endpoint where {
?target a s223:WatertoWaterHeatPump .
?target s223:contains ?prop .
?prop rdfs:label ?label .
?prop s223:observes ?qty .
?qty s223:hasExternalReference ?ref .
?ref ref:endpoint ?alc_endpoint .
?ref ref:mpc_db_name ?mpc_endpoint .
?ref ref:writable "False" .
}

PREFIX brick: <https://brickschema.org/schema/Brick/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?heatPump ?propLabel ?alcEndpoint ?mpcEndpoint
WHERE {
  # Water‑to‑Water Heat Pumps
  ?heatPump a ash:WatertoWaterHeatPump .

  # Properties associated with the heat pump
  ?heatPump ash:hasProperty ?prop .
  ?prop rdfs:label ?propLabel .

  # Restrict to non‑writable quantities (writable = "False" or not present)
  OPTIONAL { ?prop brick:writable ?writable . }
  FILTER ( !bound(?writable) || ?writable = "False"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> )

  # Endpoint references for ALC (source) and MPC (mpc_db_name)
  OPTIONAL { ?prop brick:source ?alcEndpoint . }
  OPTIONAL { ?prop brick:mpc_db_name ?mpcEndpoint . }
}
ORDER BY ?heatPump ?propLabel

ground_truth_sparql:
PREFIX ref: <https://brickschema.org/schema/Brick/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX s223: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>
SELECT DISTINCT ?target ?prop ?label ?qty ?ref ?alc_endpoint ?mpc_endpoint where {
?target a s223:WatertoWaterHeatPump .
?target s223:contains ?prop .
?prop rdfs:label ?label .
?prop s223:observes ?qty .
?qty s223:hasExternalReference ?ref .
?ref ref:endpoint ?alc_endpoint .
?ref ref:mpc_db_name ?mpc_endpoint .
?ref ref:writable "False" .
}
